About Brooches

The varied and colorful Swarovski brooch collection features exclusively designed pieces that represent one of the modern luxe brand’s most innovative forms of expression.

The Swarovski brooch collection includes refined nature-inspired pins and sparkling statement pieces, which are delicately designed to add freshness and flash to any outfit. These exceptional pieces are carefully created in rhodium and gold plating and adorned with Swarovski’s signature precision cut clear and color crystals and patented design techniques.

Blooming flowers with crystal pavé accents or rhodium-plated clear crystal pavé accents; shimmering pieces embellished with clear and color crystals or palladium-plated crystal Pointiage®, and geometric designs for every occasion are all part of this surprisingly unique collection which reflects all the wonder of nature and the beauty of light.

Worn alone or with other pieces from Swarovski’s jewelry collection, Swarovski brooches add sparkle to one’s daily attire, shine as a festive fashion accessory, or indisputable style to a contemporary woman’s wardrobe.
